#18731
A Blacksmith's Bedroom~
   This room is utilitarian with the bare minimum of comforts.  A large bed
lies with the headboard against the far wall flanked by a pair of small, oak
nightstands.  At the foot of the bed is a chamberpot that appears to be full.
The floor is bare except for a faded green rug with crusty white stains.  On a
coat rack near the door hangs several leather aprons and gloves.  
~
187 32768 0 0 0 0
D3
~
~
