S
#18732
A Blacksmith's Storage~
   A small ladder lands in a squatty little room full of metallic bars, ores,
and fluxes.  Unfortunately gold and precious metals seem to e lacking in the
wide array of choices.  The floor is covered in a fine powder of mixed metals
and little nuggets of ore.  Stacks of half finished weapons and armor line the
back wall while piles of horseshoes, nails, and other everyday hardware crowd
the rest of the room.  
~
