#18734
A Baker's Bedroom~
   This room is very obviously a sleeping quarters.  A large feather mattress
that could fit three large people sits in the center of the room.  A wash
basin lies on the left-most wall along with a rough-made wooden chest.  The
smells of the bakery drift in through the doorway.  
~
