The Ender Royal Guard Quarter's~
   Heavy curtains open to reveal six wooden frames holding thick, down
mattresses.  Each bed is tidied neatly in an otherwise stark room.  This is
the sleeping quarters for the guards.  A small wash basin and bowl sit on a
small table at the southern corner of the room.  
