#18737
The Ender Village Shaman~
   A large pile of woven blankets sits in the center of the room.  Small,
wooden shelves line each wall containing various herbal remedies and potions.
A disturbingly small table sits in the northwest corner of the room.  A ladder
sits against the shelves, apparently used frequently judging by the line dug
into the dirt floor that follows the shelves.  
